{"tid":1372672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"班牛屎佬唔係要保家衛國？做乜淨係縮係屎坑入面唔敢出黎呀？","createTime":"2019-07-27T13:19:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T04:49:36.000Z","uid":41411,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fcd419d55b1568253388a695c52dee1904a04ab4","tid":1372672,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:19:49.000Z","msg":"話緊你地班元朗牛屎佬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係大大聲要保衛家園唔比我地入黎元朗？<br />\n721無咩人就夠膽衝晒出黎無差別恐襲 以為自己好威<br />\n今日過萬人入黎元朗搵你地就淆撚到要縮係屎坑 搵黑警保護<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母男人老狗比d勇氣啦 垃圾<br />\n抵你地一世要喱埋係元朗村屋入面打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />慢慢執牛屎啦牛屎飛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">元朗圍村仔正一垃圾</span></span>"},{"pid":"a52eb7a5fc8614be5acd5c70e6884dc2fbb7d614","tid":1372672,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}